fields.question:
Evan has a list of numbers. He asks his friends to assign points to each number, depending on whether they like the number, dislike it or don’t really have an opinion. If someone likes a number, that number is assigned a point of 1, if someone dislikes a number, then the number is assigned a point of 0. If someone is neutral about the number, it is not assigned any point.
